{"tid":2492748,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"勞爾宣布請辭古巴共產黨中央委員會第一書記職務","createTime":"2021-04-17T10:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T05:44:16.000Z","uid":295230,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3dcf184f9ea0031ad34228a7b6fa9640957267","tid":2492748,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:51:04.000Z","msg":"古巴領導人勞爾周五宣布，請辭古巴共產黨中央委員會第一書記的職務。<br />\n<br />\n今年89歲的勞爾此舉，是古巴共產黨統治古巴約60年以來，該黨首次不是由卡斯特羅兄弟領導。勞爾是已故古巴領導人卡斯特羅的弟弟。<br />\n<br />\n生於1931年的勞爾，在首都哈瓦那的大學修讀經濟，其後加入共產黨少年團。他在1953年協助哥哥卡斯特羅策畫攻擊軍營，行動失敗後被判監13年，但在1955年獲特赦，流亡到墨西哥，並在當地與革命家捷古華拉結交成為朋友。<br />\n<br />\n卡斯特羅在1959年領導古巴革命，勞爾當年是指揮官之一，兄弟兩人在捷古華拉協助下，推翻美國扶植的政權。"},{"pid":"60696ba784c9002a4ff3a1b40114381e9a2d16cb","tid":2492748,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:51:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586258-20210417.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586258-20210417.htm&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLx68f20TVEdZexmFDfnZHo4%3D&h=5b21c66e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586258-20210417.htm&h=44b2ebd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586258-20210417.htm</a>"},{"pid":"47994bce90c9fbfcb495951c3889c9d0e359b947","tid":2492748,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:58:13.000Z","msg":"古巴會唔會變天呢？"},{"pid":"66fc06323cb1da15e12f1ba74d6c5c91c223515b","tid":2492748,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47994bce90c9fbfcb495951c3889c9d0e359b947","tid":2492748,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:58:13.000Z","msg":"古巴會唔會變天呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:00:02.000Z","msg":"唔太可能<br />\n古巴政局相當穩定"},{"pid":"b72a7ccd972021dc1bbe382aa844557b77c05fef","tid":2492748,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,